subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution.
Known from the east coast of 
India
and Bay of Bengal (
Wood-Mason & Alcock 1891
; 
Wood-Mason, 1892
; Alcock & Anderson, 1894; Alcock, 1896; Alcock, 1899; 
Huys et al., 2014
; Krishnamoorthy, 2009; 
Lakshimi Pillai et al., 2013
; 
Prema et al., 2018
), Arabian Sea (
Lloyd, 1907
) including 
Pakistan
(
Tirmizi & Serène, 1971
). The species occurs at depths between 
128–457 m
(Alcock, 1896, 1899; 
Lloyd, 1907
; 
Prema et al., 2018
).
